## Overview

This document tracks technical exceptions to standard patterns, workarounds for edge cases, and special handling required. These are intentional deviations that should be preserved and understood.

**Why track exceptions?**
- Prevent "fixing" intentional workarounds
- Understand why code deviates from patterns
- Know when exceptions can be removed
- Help future developers (and AI) understand the codebase

